<p>


Great East Village location with easy access to Division Blue Line stop (0.5 mi.), Chicago Avenue bars and restaurants (0.1 mi.), Division Street bars, restaurants, sidewalk cafes (0.4 mi.), Kennedy Expressway (&lt; 1 mi.) and just over 1 mile to the 606 elevated trail.
